**ALLE** Call-Sites von `attentionSignalsFromOptionRequestLike` müssen `isAgencyOnly` setzen — auch in Client-Web-Kontexten (Attention-Filter, Header-Label, Listen-Labels), Agency-Views, Kalender, Tests.

